            <p class="py-6  font-bold">SKSA International is a global association dedicated to teaching and promoting Shotokan karate and other martial arts in General.</p>
            <p class="">We were founded in 2015 by Master David Hari in Udaypur, Rajasthan, India, and Special effort by kyoshi HMNC Rana have since grown to include members in countries around the world. In 2022, our head office was relocated to the United States under the control of Master Kyoshi Dady Kassim. We believe that Martial Arts is more than just a sport or a form of self-defense - it is a way of life that promotes discipline, respect, and personal growth. Our association is committed to preserving the traditions and teachings of Shotokan karate and other martial Arts, while also embracing innovation and growth. Our members come from all walks of life and range in age and experience level. We welcome anyone who is interested in learning and practicing Martila Arts to join our association and be a part of our community. In addition to providing training and support to our members, we also host events and competitions, publish educational materials, and collaborate with other Martials organizations around the world. If you are interested in becoming a member of SKSA International, please visit our <span class="text-red-600 font-bold"><a href="/member">MEMBERSHIP PAGE</a></span> to learn more.</p>

